---
title: One-Pot Vegan Cauliflower & Bean Soup with Cilantro & Blue Corn Tortilla Chips
description: This hearty, flavorful vegan soup is ready in under 30 minutes and cooks in one pot, making cleanup a breeze! Cauliflower and beans are simmered in a richly-spiced broth—veggie stock, onion, green pepper, tomatoes, and Southwest seasonings—until tender. Garnish with fresh cilantro and serve crunchy blue corn tortilla chips alongside for a SOUP-er supper.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/one-pot-vegan-cauliflower-bean-soup-f909b58a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/one-pot-vegan-cauliflower-bean-soup-630e489862e1d857fa01c11b-2c909e8d.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/one-pot-vegan-cauliflower-bean-soup-630e489862e1d857fa01c11b
cuisine: Mexican
time required: 35 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 510 kcal
  fat: 15 g
  saturated fat: 2 g
